OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome late
OL,6,Fbright or sunny spells this evening
OL,7,Fbut heavy and perhaps thundery showers
OL,8,Faround. Overnight will see showers
OL,9,Fgradually ease with some clear
OL,10,Fintervals.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FA largely dry day with
OL,13,Fbright or sunny spells, a few showers
OL,14,Faround in the morning. Cloud and rain
OL,15,Fspreading northeastwards in the
OL,16,Fevening. Fresh southwesterly winds
OL,17,Fturning southerly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
