OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FLow
OL,6,Fcloud and rain Friday clears north to
OL,7,Fleave bright spells and showers.
OL,8,FShowers or longer spells of rain
OL,9,FSaturday. Dry with sunny periods
OL,10,FSunday. Stronger winds Friday then
OL,11,Feasing.
